---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
const title = 'Architecture Marketing Resources | IPQmedia';
const description =
  'Practical guides on lead generation, paid ads, and client acquisition for US architecture firms, from the team that builds these systems for a living.';
---

<Base title={title} description={description}>
  <h1>Architecture marketing, without the guesswork</h1>
  <p class="lede">
    Most firms still win work the slow way: referrals, repeat clients, and hoping
    the phone rings. This is the library for the firms that want a system instead.
    Real playbooks on getting found, getting leads, and turning them into signed
    high-end projects.
  </p>

  <p>
    We run client acquisition for US architecture firms every day. These guides are
    the same thinking we use when we build it for a client, written so you can act on
    it whether you hire help or do it yourself.
  </p>

  <h2>Start here</h2>
  <div class="card-grid">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Lead generation for architects</h3>
      <p>How firms build a predictable pipeline of qualified project enquiries, and what actually moves the needle versus what wastes budget. Guide coming shortly.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Meta ads for architects</h3>
      <p>What it takes to make Facebook and Instagram ads produce real consultations for an architecture practice, with the targeting and creative that works. Guide coming shortly.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Who this is for</h2>
  <p>
    Principals and partners at US architecture firms who want more of the right
    projects and less dependence on word of mouth. If that is you, these guides will
    save you months of trial and error.
  </p>

  <p>
    Want the system built for you instead of by you?
    <a href="https://ipqmedia.com/book-a-call">Book a call with IPQmedia</a>.
  </p>
</Base>
